answers.body_markdown:
In android 9, cleartext support is &quot;false&quot; by default. You need to change it to &quot;true&quot; in Manifest.xml start your url with &quot;http&quot; instead of &quot;https&quot;:

    &quot;&quot;&lt;application
        ...
        android:usesCleartextTraffic=&quot;true&quot;
        ...&gt;
        ...
    &lt;/application&gt;

